OL,3,CBrixham's month-long boil water notice
OL,4,Cto be lifted in 'phased approach'
OL,6,FSouth West Water says the boil water
OL,7,Fnotice affecting parts of Devon will
OL,8,Fbe lifted in a "phased approach",
OL,9,Ffollowing the cryptosporidium outbreak.
OL,11,FAround 2,500 homes in Brixham and
OL,12,FKingswear remain under the notice
OL,13,Fafter a parasite was found in the
OL,14,Fwater supply on 15 May.
OL,16,FThe UK Health Security Agency said the
OL,17,Fnumber of confirmed infections had
OL,18,Freached more than 100, but the rate is
OL,19,F"slowing down".
