OL,3,CBrixham's month-long boil water notice
OL,4,Cto be lifted in 'phased approach'
OL,6,FSouth West Water says it is working to
OL,7,Fclean the supply system and reinstate
OL,8,Fsafe drinking water for all properties.
OL,10,FIn a statement on the social media
OL,11,Fplatform X, formerly known as Twitter,
OL,12,Fthe company said: "We are preparing
OL,13,Ffor a phased approach to lifting the
OL,14,Fboil water notices as our progress to
OL,15,Fclean and protect the network develops.
OL,17,F"This will allow us to give people
OL,18,Faccess to clean and safe drinking
OL,19,Fwater quicker, where it is safe to do
OL,20,Fso."
