OL,3,CBrixham's month-long boil water notice
OL,4,Cto be lifted in 'phased approach'
OL,6,F"As with any other sickness bug, it is
OL,7,Freally important to follow good
OL,8,Finfection prevention measures such as
OL,9,Fhandwashing with hot soapy water, as
OL,10,Falcohol hand gel is not enough to kill
OL,11,Fcryptosporidium. This will prevent
OL,12,Ffurther cases spreading from person to
OL,13,Fperson through the community.
OL,15,F"Those with symptoms should stay off
OL,16,Fnursery, school and work for 48 hours
OL,17,Fsince the last episode of illness, and
OL,18,Fanyone with diarrhoea should not go
OL,19,Fswimming for 14 days after their last
OL,20,Fepisode of illness.
